name: Epibenthic and fish community in Gazi Bay sampled from 12-15 October 1994
description: Counts on epibenthos and fish species sampled in October 1994 by beam trawling in the mangroves andseagrass beds of GaziBay(kenya). Minimum and maximum standard length of fish was measured. The data were digitized by VLIZ fromthe original report:Boone, A. (1996).
